title: JRE REVIEW of 1306 with Wiz Khalifa
description:
Today I'm joined by my buddy Garrett who's a huge Wiz fan. Wiz Khalifa is a raper and producer. He's as big as it gets in the rap world. He has a really interesting conversation with Joe that goes into everything from how he started out to his new quest with fitness and MMA training. I Didn't know a great deal about Wiz before I went to review his podcast with Joe and I was impressed by how he thinks.

 

Enjoy my review folks!
